```python
def clip(pc, norm):
     tot_norm = 0.0
     for p in pc.parameters_list():
         tot_norm += (p.grad_as_array()**2).sum()
     tot_norm = np.sqrt(tot_norm)
     clip_coeff = norm / (tot_norm + 1e-6)
     if clip_coeff <1:
         for p in pc.parameters_list():
             p.scale_gradient(clip_coeff)
```

